                  "What line do you add to avoid the nextInt-then-nextLine skip?",
                  "An extra <code>input.nextLine();</code> after the <code>nextInt()</code> to consume the leftover newline."
                ]
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "exercise",
              "html": "Ask the user for two whole numbers and print their sum. Prompt before each read, and read with <code>nextInt()</code>.",
              "meta": "stdin: two integers · checks: prints their sum"
            }
