              "type": "callout",
              "kind": "note",
              "title": "This is your guessing game",
              "html": "The final-exam guessing game is exactly this shape: <em>loop forever → read a guess → if it's correct, break; otherwise tell them higher/lower and loop again.</em> Recognizing the pattern is half the battle."
